@startuml
' @id(DOM-ARCH-SPEC)
' @desc(DOM-ARCH-SPEC, "Implemented as the .mdd/architecture/ yml templates (templates::arch_components_template / arch_decisions_template / arch_constraints_template), scaffolded SeededOnce by mdd init (write_text_create_if_missing) and authored by /mdd-kickoff. components.yml / decisions.yml / constraints.yml are the structured what+why beside the diagrams; decisions are append-only (the file is the history); diffs are git today, a structured mdd arch verb is a follow-up.")
' Current-side domain for the architectural source of truth (cycle 0028),
' derived from the implemented .mdd/architecture/ templates + mdd init scaffold.
title Architecture source of truth (current)

class ArchitectureSpec {
  + dir : Path
}
class Component {
  + id : String
  + name : String
  + kind : ComponentKind
  + owns : List<Id>
  + dependsOn : List<Id>
  + tech : String
}
enum ComponentKind {
  service
  library
  datastore
  adapter
  ui
  external
}
class Decision {
  + id : String
  + title : String
  + status : DecisionStatus
  + date : Date
  + context : String
  + decision : String
  + consequences : String
  + supersedes : String?
  + supersededBy : String?
}
enum DecisionStatus {
  proposed
  accepted
  superseded
  deprecated
}
class Constraint {
  + id : String
  + rule : String
  + appliesTo : List<Id>
  + rationale : String
}

ArchitectureSpec "1" o-- "*" Component : components.yml >
ArchitectureSpec "1" o-- "*" Decision : decisions.yml >
ArchitectureSpec "1" o-- "*" Constraint : constraints.yml >
Component --> ComponentKind
Decision --> DecisionStatus

note bottom of Decision
  Append-only: a change supersedes a prior decision
  (supersedes / supersededBy) rather than rewriting
  it, so decisions.yml IS the decision history
  (OCL-ARCH-DECISION-HAS-STATUS,
  OCL-ARCH-SUPERSEDE-LINKED).
end note
note bottom of Component
  owns / dependsOn reference diagram @ids (DOM-/CMP-);
  components.yml stays in sync with the component
  diagrams (OCL-ARCH-COMPONENTS-IN-SYNC).
end note
@enduml
